CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 26, reads: "Champs - Members of the Ammon Center senior basketball team, winners of the Park and Recreation cage tournament, are, left to right, front row: George Brown, C. Brock, H. Martin, W. Munroe and Gerald Everett. Back row: R. Primus, P. Graves, Coach Charlie Betts, D. Graves and J. Hughes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ammon Center senior basketball team, kneeling: George Brown, C. Brock, H. Martin, W. Munroe, and Gerald Everett; standing: R. Primus, P. Graves, Coach Charlie Betts, D. Graves, and J. Hughes, posed with trophy and basketball inscribed "Champs 1956-57", another version
